Welcome to this charming move-in ready block home nestled in the heart of Tampa. This delightful property offers a plethora of features that will surely capture your attention and make you fall in love at first sight. Inside, the home boasts a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, with ceramic tile flooring throughout the home, low-maintenance, and simple to keep up. The abundance of natural light that fills the space creates a cheerful and uplifting ambiance. The bedrooms are cozy and offer a peaceful retreat at the end of a long day. The kitchen is tastefully designed, with granite countertops, wood finish cabinets, cute fixtures and finishes that exude elegance and style. Situated on a nice-sized lot, over a quarter acre of land, this home provides ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. What sets this home apart from others is the property location and the absence of HOA and deed restrictions. Say goodbye to the limitations and constraints! You have the freedom to personalize and make this home truly your own. An added bonus of having a multipurpose room; Gazebo, Cabana, Greenhouse the possibilities are endless. And a shed, this home is a rare find. Not only is it close to parks and trails, but it is also conveniently located near beaches, downtown, TPA airport, and shopping centers. Whether you're in the mood for a day at the beach, exploring the vibrant city life, or indulging in some retail therapy, everything is just a short drive away. Now is the time to make this dream home yours. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity. Call now to schedule a viewing. Your new home awaits!
